query:
WITH entities AS (
                SELECT *
                FROM bria_addresses
                WHERE account_id = $1 AND wallet_id = $2 AND kind = 'external'
                AND (COALESCE((created_at, id) > ($4, $3), $3 IS NULL))
                ORDER BY created_at, id) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, CASE WHEN $5 THEN e.context ELSE NULL::jsonb END as "context: es_entity::ContextData", e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN bria_address_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.created_at, i.id, i.id, e.sequence
